name: Seven Princes of Hell | Magnus Shaw
description:
" I hear the voices of those who fell victim to my scourge. It is not the wails and cries that pain me, it's the fact I cannot be sated further!"

- Magnus Shaw


Magnus Shaw is a high-ranking archdemon, and the chief executioner to the monarch of Hell. One of his epithets is the "Evil Genius of the Household" meaning that Magnus Shaw is the demon that conducts the most heinous, depraved, and unbearably cruel tortures in the pits of Hell. Magnus is likened to Nemesis and the destroying angel and is known as The Executioner.
